{"tid":1572644,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有無方法或暗號口號，一嗌出來，大家便出來幫手？","createTime":"2019-09-15T17:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T17:30:35.000Z","uid":170601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ad8a3c242bac1a4c58dd38e5c5384d89cd87b8","tid":1572644,"uid":170601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:26:20.000Z","msg":"例如大嗌黑警！<br />\n大家便要一湧而上去打鳩黑警？<br />\n<br />\n當然，如果兩個普通巿民，互相對罵，<br />\n但又互相大嗌暗號，<br />\n各巿民都要查清楚乜事，<br />\n如果只是同途人不和，便勸交息事寧人。<br />\n<br />\n因為眼見太多被單拖或兩三個黑警出來亂拉人，<br />\n如不作反抗，<br />\n會越來越多無辜人被拉或被自殺！"},{"pid":"81b68f093f641b6fcb3b75df073c6e9bd2bf3be6","tid":1572644,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:26:29.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[品葱轉載] [文宣戰術] 教你如何宣傳反共，緊貼現在熱門事件。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ebhFbS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ebhFbS</a>"},{"pid":"025fd29ff77999d0a3e8210eac0ab01ca61ce3e1","tid":1572644,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:30:35.000Z","msg":"915 - 進步，改善，突破<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1572164/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1572164/page/1</a>"}]}